Description: Quiet, residential area, with a spacious basement apartment, located 10 mins from the National Harbor, and 20 minutes from downtown DC. Ample street parking, full laundry, kitchen, and living spaces. Over 1500 sq. ft. of space. Please give me a call if you would like to schedule a viewing. Serious inquiries only. Ideal for small family or professionals. Pets and smoking are not allowed.

Kitchen:
* Dishwasher
* Disposal
* Ice Maker
* Microwave
* Oven
* Range
* Refrigerator
